==Romanian==

===Etymology===

===Noun===
'''pădure''', '''păduri''' {{p}} {{f}}

# [[forest]]

===Synonyms===
* [[silvă]] (rarely used)
* [[codru]]


===Derived terms===
* [[pădurar]] (noun): [[forester]]
* [[pădurice]] (noun): small forrest
* a [[împăduri]] (verb): to [[forrest]]
* [[împădurit]] {{m}}, [[împădurită]] {{f}}, [[împădurite]] {{p}} (adj): (of a place) to be [[forested]], to be covered with forest
* [[păduros]] {{m}}, [[păduroasă]] {{f}}, [[păduroase]] {{p}} (adj): (of a place) to be [[forested]], to be like a forest, ? [[woody]]

'''Note'''

The adjective pertaining to forest is not derived from this word, but rather from the synonym [[silvă]] as:
* [[silvic]] {{m}}, [[silvică]] {{f}}, [[silvice]] {{p}}
* [[silvatic]] {{m}}, [[silvatică]] {{f}}, [[silvatice]] {{p}}
* e.g. road through the forest: drum silvic (and not "drum păduros")
